name: string 'multi'
description:
Treat youself to the one and only string 'multi'!! 

Here in all-white for the marriage-season, with beautiful cotton-made gift-packaging and illustrated instruction-card.

The string itself is made from a soft tulle (Polyamide and Lycra), the double-sided satin-ribbon is 100 polyester with a silky touch.

The ribbon can be completely detached from the string and offers endless ribboning-possibilities at 3m40, enjoy!

This product is made in Poland, design, quality-control, printing and shipping happens in Paris, France.
